Create Tooltips for Repeater Widgets
For a quick review of related data while reviewing metrics in a scrollable layout, add tooltips to a repeater. You can design a separate tooltip for text, numbers, images, and bullet, gauge, polar gauge, or flat gauge charts in the repeater.

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS
Create and Edit Analytics Dashboards

To customize dashboard widgets:
In the dashboard designer, with the repeater widget selected, click Edit Repeater Content.
Select the widget to which you want to add the tooltip, and then click Tooltip.
Set tooltip content and its size. Preview the tooltip when done.
Use a similar process to create tooltips for other widgets in the repeater widget.
Preview your changes and save your dashboard.
title: Customizing Dashboard Widgets with Tooltips
